68% per annum and a seven-year maturity. We intend to use the", "bbox": [150.0, 1063.2, 1061.7, 1084.1]}, {"text": "proceeds of the notes to acquire properties, to fund development and redevelopment activities and for general", "bbox": [150.0, 1088.2, 1063.5, 1109.1]}, {"text": "corporate purposes.", "bbox": [150.0, 1113.2, 313.3, 1134.1]}, {"text": "On February 27, 2009, we notified the lenders under our mortgage agreement with respect to 350 East Cermak", "bbox": [191.7, 1163.2, 1115.8, 1184.1]}, {"text": "Road that we will repay in full the outstanding principal balance, accrued interest and other fees due on the loan on", "bbox": [150.0, 1188.2, 1110.4, 1209.1]}, {"text": "March 9, 2009. We expect to finance the repayment with approximately $97.0 million in borrowings under our", "bbox": [150.0, 1213.2, 1076.6, 1234.1]}, {"text": "revolving credit facility.", "bbox": [150.0, 1238.2, 352.3, 1259.1]}, {"text": "109", "bbox": [621.9, 1484.1, 653.1, 1504.9]}]}